 ' '.escapeshellarg($this->full_src_path).' '.escapeshellarg($this->full_dst_path).' 2>&1';\r\n\r\nalso this library in general has problem\r\nwhen used config for image processing \r\ni.e.\r\n$config['source_image']\t= './folder/path/'.$upload_info['file_name'];\r\n$config['new_image'] ='./folder/path/'.$upload_info['file_name'];\r\ncompiles the $this->full_scr_path & $this->full_dst_path in the image_lib.php in initialise correctly in earlier version\r\nbut in latest version for above conf the path compile as \r\n\r\n$this->full_scr_path = correct absolute path converted and set here\r\n$this->full_dst_path = incorrect absolute path i.e exact value of './folder/path/'.$upload_info['file_name']; which no good thus resulting in wrong commands\r\n\r\nso had to modify them to \r\n$config['source_image']\t='./folder/path/'.$upload_info['file_name'];\r\n$config['new_image'] = FCPATH.'./folder/path/'.$upload_info['file_name']; which is inconsistent with the docs\r\n\r\n**so two problems namely,**\r\n1. space issue\r\n2. relative directory not set properly in full_dst_path when used new_image config varible\r\n\r\n","closed_by":{"login":"narfbg","id":1058011,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEwNTgwMTE=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1058011?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg","html_url":"https://github.com/narfbg","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/received_events","type":"User